fields.description:
When a user runs an API call for JIRA Cloud, the errors returned appear in the format below:

{code:java}
{"errorMessages":["No project could be found with key 'TEST2'."],"errors":{}}
{code}

instead of this more common format:
{code}
 {"errors": {"errors": ["errors"],"errorMessages": ["messages"]}}
{code}

Can this be improved to match the commonly used trend to avoid confusion.
